Question: Are both sides of the sandwich made with the same kind of bread?

Reference Answer: yes

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/549887.jpg

Original program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='bread')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='What kind of bread is this?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='What kind of bread is this?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == {ANSWER1} else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
